parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the passenger airbag sensor can cause the airbag system to malfunction, potentially leading to the failure of the airbag to deploy in the event of an accident, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: the airbag light turns on and off intermittently
the airbag system service indicator light appears
the passenger airbag light is not lit when a passenger is present
the airbag system malfunctions when a passenger is present
the airbag system fails to deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the side detection system can cause the loss of various safety features, including blind spot warnings, airbags, and turn signals, which can lead to accidents or unsafe driving conditions.
symptoms: The side detection system warning light comes on

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the intake cam solenoid valve can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or unsafe driving conditions.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
and the vehicle may shut off while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can cause the airbag to deploy unnecessarily or fail to deploy in the event of an accident, leading to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The passenger airbag is on when no passenger is present
and the airbag may not deploy in the event of an accident.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various safety features to malfunction, leading to accidents or unsafe driving conditions.
symptoms: and warning lights appear on the dashboard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The fire hazard can cause damage to the vehicle and potentially lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: A fire starts in the vehicle

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission control module can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: the transmission control module warning light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unintended acceleration can cause the vehicle to accelerate independently, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates independently without warning
the brake pedal is depressed to stop the unintended acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Harsh gear shifting can cause the vehicle to jolt, leading to accidents or injuries.
